Class HtmlTemplateExporter

org.apache.jmeter.report.dashboard.HtmlTemplateExporter
All Implemented Interfaces:
DataExporter
public class HtmlTemplateExporter extends AbstractDataExporter
The class HtmlTemplateExporter provides a data exporter that generates and processes template files using freemarker.
